text: Hana Maciuchová (29 November 1945 – 26 January 2021) was a Czech actress. She was born in Šternberk, Czechoslovakia. Maciuchová was known for her roles in Chalupáři (1975), Prázdniny pro psa (1980), Krkonošské pohádky (1984), In the Coat of Lioness' Arms (1994), Loners (2000), Ulice (2005-2015) and Dobrá čtvrť (2008).
